articles.title: Lee nabs bronze in uneven bars for sixth medal - ESPN
articles.description: American gymnast Suni Lee won her sixth Olympic medal with an individual bronze in the uneven bars, finishing behind Algeria's Kyalia Nemour and China's Qui Qiyuan.
